profile:
Imperial Roofs were awarded the Vaughan Citizen Readers Choice Award in 2011

In 1968 my father founded Cel Marchildon Roofing, which has grown into the company we have today.  Through commitment to excellence in our workmanship and materials we have built our reputation of TOTAL CUSTOMER SATISFACTION by providing our customers with the BEST ROOFING SYSTEM that will accommodate their needs and budget.  We will provide you, our valued customer, with a detailed assessment that will outline the specific requirements for your home. 

Our expert staff is committed to providing you with the BEST ROOFING EXPERIENCE available in the GTA.  All workers are covered by WORKERS COMPENSATION.  Our company is fully LICENSED AND INSURED to provide you with a WORRY FREE ROOFING EXPERIENCE.  We DO NOT USE ROOFING SUB-CONTRACTORS.  All work is performed by our expert employees. 

This may or may not be your first time purchasing a new roof, however we would like to outline some of the key factors in our operating process:

?	Provide a copy of our Insurance Certificate
?	Provide a copy of Workplace Insurance Safety Board Certificate upon request
?	Provide a copy of our Operating License 
?	Protect your home and surrounding area from falling debris
?	Tear off all old shingles to the roof deck
?	Inspect the wood deck for rotting and warping areas
?	Install eave protection to all insulated eaves 
?	Install name brand shingles with your choice 25 years to limited lifetime guarantee
?	Install proper ventilation to the roof (1sq ft for every 300 sq ft of attic floor area) 
?	Install new metal flashing where needed or refurbish to “new” standards
?	Install closed valleys with aluminum underneath to ensure maximum protection 
?	Full property clean up using magnetic sweeps and trailers to ensure no driveway damage
?	All employees are Fall Safety accredited and Crew Chief First Aid and CPR trained

Services We Provide:
*Asphalt Shingle Replacement
*Gutters, Soffit & Fascia
*Siding - Vinyl, Aluminum
*Leaf Screen for Eavestroughs
*Rooftop Snow & Ice Dam Removal
*Roof Repairs
*Roof Evaluations
*Cedar Shakes
*Slate Roofs
*Insurance Claims
*Ventilation Upgrades

profile:
Solid Eavestrough is your one stop shop for all eavestrough services in Toronto and GTA area. We provide all the essential eavestrough cleaning and maintenance services that homeowners need to keep their eavestrough clean and waterproof. Serving areas: Toronto, Etobicoke, Markham, Mississauga, Richmond Hill, Scarborough, Vaughan, Thornhill, Woodbridge.



*****

Cleaning your eaves is one of the most important things you can do to maintain the beauty and value of your home. When eavestroughs are full of leaves and debris they become heavy and get pulled off pitch. This can result in damage to the fascia and soffit areas. As water overflows it leaks behind the eaves and can travel into your home damaging walls and timber.

*****

Eaves cleaning and repair plays a vital role in the maintenance and protection of your home. They are part of the rainwater drainage system that helps prevent:

*****

Foundation Damage
Soffit and Fascia Rot
Spalling Brickwork
Internal Damp and Mold Growth
Termite, Mosquito and Rodent Infestations
Landscape Destruction

Any of these problems can be costly and time consuming to fix. Consistent maintenance is critical to keep your home dry. Let our Toronto eavestrough cleaning professionals give you peace of mind when dealing with your eaves or roof problems.

CityPro Aluminum & Contracting Inc. was founded in 2000 by two young entrepreneurs to establish and continuously improve and maintain the industry's high standards. With over 10 years in the business, we are committed to integrity and ethical standards in supplying GTA with the best aluminum-siding products and services. Our goal is to provide top-quality workmanship and excellent customer service. In order to achieve this, we use highly trained installers and the best quality aluminum out there from the best suppliers. This allows us to provide 100% warranty on our work and materials.

*****

Quality, commitment and the promise of product longevity are the core philosophies of CityPro Aluminum & Contracting. All of our installations are warranted for life, if any sort of failure does occur we will fix or replace the defect, free of charge for as long as you own the home.
We carry a $2,000,000 Liability insurance to make sure safety is our top priority. All of our workers are covered by WSIB workers compensation. If we get hurt on your property, you’re not liable in any way. Copies supplied upon request.
CityPro Aluminum & Contracting covers the entire Greater Toronto area. If you decide to move forward with us, we’ll write a detailed agreement including all the specifications we discussed. Most projects are completed within 2 to 3 weeks of the agreement. We won’t accept final payment until you are 100% satisfied.

profile:
City roofing and aluminum co. has been in business since 1994, over all these years, our extreme commitment to excellence and customer service make us one of the most trusted name in the roofing industry.
Our roofing department offers residential and commercial services including re-roofing; new roof construction and retro-fitting, we install a wide range of materials such as asphalt shingles, metal roofing, composite roof and cedar wood shakes.
Our aluminum department offers complete aluminum product.s and sheet metal work, our crews utilizes state of art tools and equipment to install aluminum soffit, fascia, seamless eavestrough and rainware accessories.
What’s more, in addition to providing re-roofing services and new construction work, we also offer roofing repair services, on-going maintenance service, and roofing inspection consultations.  These services are designed to extend the life of your roof by identifying and fixing the minor problems before they become major issues.

profile:
Assured Quality Roofing provides roofing and eavestrough services in the GTA for residential and commercial clients. Exceeding Ontario’s building code standards. Excellent customer satisfaction 25 years.

***
 
The reason people choose us over any of our competition is simple; We use the best materials, tradesmen and deliver the best in service and quality. Our tradesmen are paid according to the quality of work, rather than on the speed with which they do the job. This ensures top quality over a speedy job. It is far more important to us to do the job correctly and have a happy customer who recommends us to their friends. You have our guarantee that we will do the job right the first time. 

***
 
We never settle for the minimum building code standards it doesn’t cost a lot to go from a minimum building code standard to exceeding the building code standards. The owner is on every job site and has personally over seen thousands of jobs to a successful conclusion. You will be talking directly with the owner about the work you want done and any of the concerns you have. We also have a list of previous customers should you wish to have references.

profile:
Topflight Aluminum is dedicated to providing quality construction and exceptional customer service. We strive to build lifelong relationships with our customers and to exceed your expectations, in every aspect of the job, from start to finish.
We’ve helped thousands of people improve the look and quality of their homes and businesses. We are proud to serve Toronto (GTA), Etobicoke, North York, Scarborough, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Markham, Stouffville, King City, Aurora, York Region, Mississauga, Oakville, Hamilton residents with expert craftsmanship and professionalism. We pride ourselves on being able to exceed the expectations of our customers.

•	WHY TopFlight Aluminum?

1.	Quality first, Speed second
We all like our issues to be resolved efficiently when contacting a company, but what will make you use Topflight Aluminum again and again? There is only one answer. The quality of the service!

2.	Great Customer Service
We understand that building or remodeling a home is a major investment, so for us it is important that our customers feel valued. Topflight Aluminum pays special attention to what our clients want, we remember the details no matter how insignificant and deliver quality services at all times.

3.	Top Quality Materials
Apart from good workmanship and top-grade professionals handling your building project, the best quality of materials we use will be next most important factor in determining the outcome of your building.

4.	Warranty

Building your dream house shouldn’t be a nightmare! That’s why we only use guaranteed products and materials with 30- to 50-year warranties. Additionally, all of our work comes with workmanship warranty. Whether you are replacing or repairing, Topflight Aluminum can always meet your needs!

OUR MISSION
Our goal is simple… To perform for our customers the highest level of quality construction services at fair and market competitive prices. We aim to maintain the highest levels of professionalism, integrity, honesty and fairness in our relationships with our suppliers, subcontractors, professional associates and customers.





GET A FREE QUOTE
No unexpected charges —see exactly what your home needs with a free estimate.

profile:
At Andy Aluminum, we've been offering complete aluminum siding, eavestrough, fascia, and soffit services to customers in Toronto, ON and the GTA for almost two decades, our four man team is composed of highly trained and dedicated professionals who are able to diagnose and resolve all of your eavestrough related problems.

Your eavestrough is an integral part of your home water management system and it is crucial that it be installed and operate properly in order to avoid water damage to your home.

Installing and repairing gutters, soffit and fascia has always been and continues to be the mainstay of our company but in addition, we also offer aluminum and vinyl siding installation, window capping, aluminum flashing and leaf guards installations.

profile:
Hello, 

My name is Tommy Hrstic and I am the owner of Sunrise Aluminum.  I have 20 years of hands on experience in the industry, and Sunrise Aluminum has been serving the greater Toronto area and beyond for more than 15 years and counting.  We specialize in seamless aluminum eaves trough installations, along with large square downspouts which has been the industry standard for the vast majority of residential homes and many commercial properties over the past decade.  We have remained a small company and all your interactions will be be with me directly and all our work is done or overseen by me personally to ensure the highest quality and customer satisfaction.  We use only the highest quality materials and aluminum purchased from reputable suppliers (Gentek and Kaycan) with many colours and materials to chose from.  

At Sunrise Aluminum we have always placed customer satisfaction as our number one priority, and have had continued success mostly thanks to their positive feedback and referrals.  With us you can always expect top quality product and workmanship for a fair price, and you can always count on us to complete your job in a timely manner as we pride ourselves in our commitment to punctuality, efficiency, and reliability.  

Contact us for a free estimate and consultation, we look forward to working with you.


Tommy Hrstic
Sunrise Aluminum

profile:
Iranda Aluminum has specialized in eavestrough cleaning, repair and installation since 2018. It has since been our goal to provide customer satisfaction 100% of the time to every one of our clients.
Iranda Aluminum  is a family run boutique aluminum company.We separate ourselves from our competition through our honesty, versatility and integrity.
We treat your property like it’s our own.We only offer services that you require. Iranda Aluminum will not up-sell you on a replacement if a much more cost effective repair is all that you require. We warranty our repairs, sometimes for as long as others warranty their installations.
We are one of the few companies in Toronto that offer cleaning, repair and replacement services. You will be hard pressed to find an eaves cleaning company that does installations, and an installation company that does cleanings. Here at Iranda Aluminum  we do it all.
Having worked in Toronto for almost  4 years, Iranda Aluminum  has, through hard work, established one of the best reputations in the industry. We have achieved this by standing behind our work and taking pride in our expertise and handiwork.
The aluminum landscape in Toronto is vast with many players offering many things.We understand that attention to detail is key when dealing with someone’s home. We are a leader in our industry when it comes to providing one of the best customer service experiences.Your satisfaction is one of our main goals.Iranda Aluminum  can say without a doubt we have never left a client unsatisfied.We strive to provide our clients with the best possible contractor experience.

once completing high school, I knew that I wanted to become a construction worker because I was very eager to learn how machines worked and how things were built. After completing my training at local 506, I started working in restoration and waterproofing. I learned different methods on how to repair damaged concrete and waterproofing. profile:
We are the highest quality gutter service company in Sacramento. We have been working for years to build our brands & develop our presence in Sacramento. We aim to be the biggest & best gutter service company in all of Sacramento, California. Clients continue to call us every year to provide quality service, because they know how hard it is to find a company that stands above the rest. When it comes to preventive maintenance there are no short cuts, the best service will deliver the best results.

We are a full service company with gutter services including repairs, replacement & of course gutter cleaning. Our staff delivers the highest quality of service & work. We work to ensure your home is completely protected being a general contractor in the State of California. We are held to the highest standards and maintain the proper insurance & bonding as required by Sacramento & California. Our clients often find that our service exceeds the standard gutter cleaner or repair individual. Our work is performed with the intention of protecting your home from future damage & repairing minor damage before it becomes a serious issue with a hefty bill. When we notice an issue we bring it to the client immediately. We explain the situation and the effects neglecting the issue may cause their home & their family. Gutter cleaning & repair are very important in Sacramento. As our weather has changed drastically over the years from flooding to droughts. When the weather does change those who have sown the field will reap the rewards of being prepared.

You find the companies who take pride in their work & service stand above the rest. Our clients call us year after year to receive the best service available. They understand the importance having a company that does quality work & delivers their service with compassion for their clients. We think of every client like family, deserving of our best, and we deliver. They find that many companies in Sacramento provide sub-par service feeling as if they are there to receive a check. Our staff is reminded every morning they are there to help take care of a client & their needs. This is why so many of our clients call us for various services.

We have expanded our preventative maintenance services division recently to provide our clients with a wide array of services, so our clients can sleep sound with the fact our company is protecting the most important assets in their life their home & their family.
